Durban - The handing over of the Mayibuye Game Reserve to the community of  kwaXimba in the Umkhambathini Local Municipality quickly soured when protesters arrived at the event on Thursday morning.

The scene was set for Deputy Minister of Environmental Affairs, Barbara Thomson, to officially launch and hand over the reserve, however a group of irate community members had other ideas.














